B048C001V000	48	1	0	Paul’s Gospel, received not from the Jerusalem Apostles, but from Jesus Christ
B048C001V011	48	1	11	For I would have you know, brothers, that the gospel that was preached by me is not man's gospel.
B048C001V012	48	1	12	For I did not receive it from any man, nor was I taught it, but I received it through a revelation of Jesus Christ.
