B048C002V000	48	2	0	The Conflict about the Truth of the Gospel:  Conflict with Cephas in Antioch
B048C002V011	48	2	11	But when Cephas came to Antioch, I opposed him to his face, because he stood condemned.
B048C002V012	48	2	12	For before 
B048C002V013	48	2	13	And the rest of the Jews acted hypocritically along with him, so that even Barnabas was led astray by their hypocrisy.
B048C002V014	48	2	14	But when I saw that their conduct was not in step with the truth of the gospel, I said to Cephas before them all, "If you, though a Jew, live like a Gentile and not like a Jew, how can you force the Gentiles to live like Jews?"
