B048C003V000	48	3	0	The Spirit and Miraculous Powers are received by faith, not by Works of the Law
B048C003V001	48	3	1	O foolish Galatians! Who has bewitched you? It was before your eyes that Jesus Christ was publicly portrayed as crucified.
B048C003V002	48	3	2	Let me ask you only this: Did you receive the Spirit by works of the law or by hearing with faith?
B048C003V003	48	3	3	Are you so foolish? Having begun by the Spirit, are you now being perfected by the flesh?
B048C003V004	48	3	4	Did you suffer so many things in vain- if indeed it was in vain?
B048C003V005	48	3	5	Does he who supplies the Spirit to you and works miracles among you do so by works of the law, or by hearing with faith-
